title: Thai Vegan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Thai, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out
description: Shop formerly operated as Thai Teak then added this little vegan eatery in Apr 2011. Cooks vegan food but from time to time sells packaged snacks that are not vegan (check label). Primarily takeaway with a few wooden tables and tall stools for seating. Most dishes offered with vegetables, tofu, or add-on mock meat.
